                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "action_type": {
                        "type": "stat_block_section",
                        "subtype": "action_type",
                        "name": "One Action"
                    },
                    "effect": "You pull a link from the armor, which transforms into a  *+1 striking dagger*  . The dagger disappears and reappears as a link in the armor after you Strike with it, or at the end of this turn if you don't make a Strike. You can Activate the blade byrnie in place of an Interact action to draw a weapon for abilities such as the Quick Draw feat. Upgrading the runes on the  *blade byrnie* makes the daggers pulled from it more powerful. The daggers have a  *+2 weapon potency* rune if the armor has a  *+2 armor potency* rune, or a  *+3 weapon potency* rune if the armor has a  *+3 armor potency* rune.",
                    "links": [
                        {
                            "type": "link",
                            "name": "striking",
